subproject.description:
1-Putting Samoa on a sustainable pathway towards transition from Least Developed Country status to Middle-Income Country status including through development of a pro-poor trade Sector Plan; Pro-Poor Policy Options paper; and a MDG Accelration Programme.
2-Support implementation of MDG programmes and monitoring of MDGs Achievement focusing in particular.

subproject.title: SAM MDGs Acceleration Project
